file inclusion:

#include <file-name>
#include "file-name"

macro definitions:

#define identifier value
#define identifier(variables) value 
#undef identifier


conditional compilation:

#if condition

#ifdef identifier
#ifndef identifier

#else
#endif

the flag "-E" only preprocess the code
> gcc -E main.c


whilst using macros always use parentheses and only feed them simple arguments to avoid errors!!!

__FILE__ gives current file name
__LINE__ gives current line number
_WIN32 is defined when compiling for windows